Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:24.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.31,0:26:28.53,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A site for anyone against the vulgar\Nero-manga artist, Hayabe Aruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:36.37,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Haruru-san? Haruru-san, please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.28,0:26:39.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Please, stop. You're bothering my neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.62,0:26:45.50,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Kazuya-san, I can't draw manga anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:48.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I just don't know what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.21,0:26:55.22,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I brought surveys.\NThere's hate mail and other fan letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.59,0:26:57.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Why'd you bring them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.43,0:27:00.68,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's so that you can decide what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.56,0:27:04.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I like your current manga style.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.64,0:27:09.69,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The difference between me and them\Nis how much we liked your previous and current style.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.69,0:27:15.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I want you to read these letters, get a feel for\Nwhat your readers want, and get back on track!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.24,0:27:20.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,These postcards are to get you started.\NAfter that, it's all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.95,0:27:22.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Up to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.58,0:27:26.88,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to the office,\NI still have some work left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.67,0:27:39.89,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One week. If she doesn't come back\Nin one week, you need to give up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.14,0:27:43.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That week's almost up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.02,0:27:48.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.69,0:27:51.77,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I've decided to keep drawing\Nero-manga from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.32,0:27:53.78,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Haruru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.78,0:27:58.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I won't falter anymore.\NI want to draw ero-manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.07,0:27:59.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Haruru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.78,0:28:04.16,Hardsub,,15,0,10,,{\an1}half a year later
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.04,0:28:04.29,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.54,0:28:07.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's Ayabe Haruru's first manga volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.00,0:28:14.05,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There are so many pre-orders,\NNao-san's having trouble keeping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.88,0:28:17.80,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You wanna sit on a bench or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.80,0:28:20.30,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How about we sit over there\Nif you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.23,0:28:28.60,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Kazuya-san, a lot's happened, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.60,0:28:29.81,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.52,0:28:33.44,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.44,0:28:34.82,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.40,0:28:36.40,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.40,0:28:43.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's something I decided I'd do if my\Nmanga volume was well-received by the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.16,0:28:46.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Half a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.75,0:28:50.58,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I felt like it was impossible to regain my fans' trust
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.58,0:28:53.34,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,after they all began saying that I'd betrayed them,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.34,0:28:56.21,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,when I thought I was actually making them happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.21,0:29:00.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You helped me through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.55,0:29:04.10,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You believed in me as a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.93,0:29:09.94,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That's why on that day,\NI yelled out that I wanted to draw ero-manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.69,0:29:14.48,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I said the same thing the day I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.78,0:29:18.11,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The only reason I was able to\Ncome this far is because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.78,0:29:24.12,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for really,\Ntruly caring about me until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.49,0:29:28.12,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,"Until now?" That makes it sound like\NI'm gonna stop caring about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.12,0:29:32.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We're going to keep making\Nero-manga together, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.46,0:29:35.13,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.75,0:29:38.42,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,By the way, about my pen name...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.42,0:29:39.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Wh-What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.97,0:29:44.14,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I was planning on having\Nmy last name changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.72,0:29:45.64,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Wait, does that mean...
